    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Image Filter Information\n\nüñºÔ∏è **Image Format Note** \n\nThis workflow is preset to find and process `.png` images from your Google Drive folder (using MIME type `image/png`).\n\nIf you're using other image formats (e.g., JPG, GIF), you'll need to update the **'Filter: Only Images'** node.\n\nSpecifically, change the filter condition from `image/png` to the correct MIME type for your image files (e.g., `image/jpeg` for JPGs).",
        "height": 600,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 6
      },
      "id": "e1e1bb1f-d73e-4dd5-b665-e669b5c343b1",
      "name": "Sticky Note3",
